<p>The minimum age required to apply for the AAI Apprentice Recruitment is <strong>18 years</strong>, and the maximum age limit is <strong>26 years as on 31 March 2026</strong>. Age relaxation will be provided to candidates belonging to <strong>SC, ST, OBC, PwBD and other reserved categories</strong> as per Government of India rules.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>AAI NR Apprentice Recruitment 2026 Selection Process</strong></h2>



